{
  "ayahs": [{
    "verseId": "1",
    "ayahText": "\u0648\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0634\u0651\u064e\u0645\u0652\u0633\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0636\u064f\u062d\u0670\u0649\u0647\u064e\u0627\u06d6 \ufd3f \u06f1 \ufd3e",
    "indoText": "Demi matahari dan sinarnya pada pagi hari,",
    "enText": "By the sun and its brightness",
    "readText": "wasy-syamsi wa \u1e0du\u1e25\u0101h\u0101",
    "surah_info": "(Qs.Asy-Syams 91:1)",
    "audio": "https:\/\/everyayah.com\/data\/Alafasy_64kbps\/091001.mp3"
  }, {
    "verseId": "2",
    "ayahText": "\u0648\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0652\u0642\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0631\u0650 \u0627\u0650\u0630\u064e\u0627 \u062a\u064e\u0644\u0670\u0649\u0647\u064e\u0627\u06d6 \ufd3f \u06f2 \ufd3e",
    "indoText": "demi bulan apabila mengiringinya,",
    "enText": "And [by] the moon when it follows it",
    "readText": "wal-qamari i\u017c\u0101 tal\u0101h\u0101",
    "surah_info": "(Qs.Asy-Syams 91:2)",
    "audio": "https:\/\/everyayah.com\/data\/Alafasy_64kbps\/091002.mp3"
  }, {
    "verseId": "3",
    "ayahText": "\u0648\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064e\u0627\u0631\u0650 \u0627\u0650\u0630\u064e\u0627 \u062c\u064e\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0649\u0647\u064e\u0627\u06d6 \ufd3f \u06f3 \ufd3e",
    "indoText": "demi siang apabila menampakkannya,",
    "enText": "And [by] the day when it displays it",
    "readText": "wan-nah\u0101ri i\u017c\u0101 jall\u0101h\u0101",
    "surah_info": "(Qs.Asy-Syams 91:3)",
    "audio": "https:\/\/everyayah.com\/data\/Alafasy_64kbps\/091003.mp3"
  }, {
    "verseId": "4",
    "ayahText": "\u0648\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0651\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0644\u0650 \u0627\u0650\u0630\u064e\u0627 \u064a\u064e\u063a\u0652\u0634\u0670\u0649\u0647\u064e\u0627\u06d6 \ufd3f \u06f4 \ufd3e",
    "indoText": "demi malam apabila menutupinya (gelap gulita),",
    "enText": "And [by] the night when it covers it",
    "readText": "wal-laili i\u017c\u0101 yagsy\u0101h\u0101",
    "surah_info": "(Qs.Asy-Syams 91:4)",
    "audio": "https:\/\/everyayah.com\/data\/Alafasy_64kbps\/091004.mp3"
  }, {
    "verseId": "5",
    "ayahText": "\u0648\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0633\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0627\u06e4\u0621\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0628\u064e\u0646\u0670\u0649\u0647\u064e\u0627\u06d6 \ufd3f \u06f5 \ufd3e",
    "indoText": "demi langit serta pembinaannya (yang menakjubkan),",
    "enText": "And [by] the sky and He who constructed it",
    "readText": "was-sam\u0101`i wa m\u0101 ban\u0101h\u0101",
    "surah_info": "(Qs.Asy-Syams 91:5)",
    "audio": "https:\/\/everyayah.com\/data\/Alafasy_64kbps\/091005.mp3"
  }, {
    "verseId": "6",
    "ayahText": "\u0648\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0652\u0627\u064e\u0631\u0652\u0636\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0637\u064e\u062d\u0670\u0649\u0647\u064e\u0627\u06d6 \ufd3f \u06f6 \ufd3e",
    "indoText": "demi bumi serta penghamparannya,",
    "enText": "And [by] the earth and He who spread it",
    "readText": "wal-ar\u1e0di wa m\u0101 \u1e6da\u1e25\u0101h\u0101",
    "surah_info": "(Qs.Asy-Syams 91:6)",
    "audio": "https:\/\/everyayah.com\/data\/Alafasy_64kbps\/091006.mp3"
  }, {
    "verseId": "7",
    "ayahText": "\u0648\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0641\u0652\u0633\u064d \u0648\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0633\u064e\u0648\u0651\u0670\u0649\u0647\u064e\u0627\u06d6 \ufd3f \u06f7 \ufd3e",
    "indoText": "demi jiwa serta penyempurnaan (ciptaan)nya,",
    "enText": "And [by] the soul and He who proportioned it",
    "readText": "wa nafsiw wa m\u0101 saww\u0101h\u0101",
    "surah_info": "(Qs.Asy-Syams 91:7)",
    "audio": "https:\/\/everyayah.com\/data\/Alafasy_64kbps\/091007.mp3"
  }, {
    "verseId": "8",
    "ayahText": "\u0641\u064e\u0627\u064e\u0644\u0652\u0647\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0647\u064e\u0627 \u0641\u064f\u062c\u064f\u0648\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0647\u064e\u0627 \u0648\u064e\u062a\u064e\u0642\u0652\u0648\u0670\u0649\u0647\u064e\u0627\u06d6 \ufd3f \u06f8 \ufd3e",
    "indoText": "maka Dia mengilhamkan kepadanya (jalan) kejahatan dan ketakwaannya,",
    "enText": "And inspired it [with discernment of] its wickedness and its righteousness,",
    "readText": "fa al-hamah\u0101 fuj\u1ee5rah\u0101 wa taqw\u0101h\u0101",
    "surah_info": "(Qs.Asy-Syams 91:8)",
    "audio": "https:\/\/everyayah.com\/data\/Alafasy_64kbps\/091008.mp3"
  }, {
    "verseId": "9",
    "ayahText": "\u0642\u064e\u062f\u0652 \u0627\u064e\u0641\u0652\u0644\u064e\u062d\u064e \u0645\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0632\u064e\u0643\u0651\u0670\u0649\u0647\u064e\u0627\u06d6 \ufd3f \u06f9 \ufd3e",
    "indoText": "sungguh beruntung orang yang menyucikannya (jiwa itu),",
    "enText": "He has succeeded who purifies it,",
    "readText": "qad afla\u1e25a man zakk\u0101h\u0101",
    "surah_info": "(Qs.Asy-Syams 91:9)",
    "audio": "https:\/\/everyayah.com\/data\/Alafasy_64kbps\/091009.mp3"
  }, {
    "verseId": "10",
    "ayahText": "\u0648\u064e\u0642\u064e\u062f\u0652 \u062e\u064e\u0627\u0628\u064e \u0645\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062f\u064e\u0633\u0651\u0670\u0649\u0647\u064e\u0627\u06d7 \ufd3f \u06f1\u06f0 \ufd3e",
    "indoText": "dan sungguh rugi orang yang mengotorinya.",
    "enText": "And he has failed who instills it [with corruption].",
    "readText": "wa qad kh\u0101ba man dass\u0101h\u0101",
    "surah_info": "(Qs.Asy-Syams 91:10)",
    "audio": "https:\/\/everyayah.com\/data\/Alafasy_64kbps\/091010.mp3"
  }, {
    "verseId": "11",
    "ayahText": "\u0643\u064e\u0630\u0651\u064e\u0628\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u062b\u064e\u0645\u064f\u0648\u0652\u062f\u064f \u0628\u0650\u0637\u064e\u063a\u0652\u0648\u0670\u0649\u0647\u064e\u0627\u0653 \u06d6 \ufd3f \u06f1\u06f1 \ufd3e",
    "indoText": "(Kaum) samud telah mendustakan (rasulnya) karena mereka melampaui batas (zalim),",
    "enText": "Thamud denied [their prophet] by reason of their transgression,",
    "readText": "ka\u017c\u017caba\u1e61 \u1e61am\u1ee5du bi\u1e6dagw\u0101h\u0101",
    "surah_info": "(Qs.Asy-Syams 91:11)",
    "audio": "https:\/\/everyayah.com\/data\/Alafasy_64kbps\/091011.mp3"
  }, {
    "verseId": "12",
    "ayahText": "\u0627\u0650\u0630\u0650 \u0627\u0646\u0652\u06e2\u0628\u064e\u0639\u064e\u062b\u064e \u0627\u064e\u0634\u0652\u0642\u0670\u0649\u0647\u064e\u0627\u06d6 \ufd3f \u06f1\u06f2 \ufd3e",
    "indoText": "ketika bangkit orang yang paling celaka di antara mereka,",
    "enText": "When the most wretched of them was sent forth.",
    "readText": "i\u017cimba'a\u1e61a asyq\u0101h\u0101",
    "surah_info": "(Qs.Asy-Syams 91:12)",
    "audio": "https:\/\/everyayah.com\/data\/Alafasy_64kbps\/091012.mp3"
  }, {
    "verseId": "13",
    "ayahText": "\u0641\u064e\u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0647\u064f\u0645\u0652 \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0652\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u0650 \u0646\u064e\u0627\u0642\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0642\u0652\u064a\u0670\u0647\u064e\u0627\u06d7 \ufd3f \u06f1\u06f3 \ufd3e",
    "indoText": "lalu Rasul Allah (Saleh) berkata kepada mereka, \u201c(Biarkanlah) unta betina dari Allah ini dengan minumannya.\u201d",
    "enText": "And the messenger of Allah [Salih] said to them, \"[Do not harm] the she-camel of Allah or [prevent her from] her drink.\"",
    "readText": "fa q\u0101la lahum ras\u1ee5lull\u0101hi n\u0101qatall\u0101hi wa suqy\u0101h\u0101",
    "surah_info": "(Qs.Asy-Syams 91:13)",
    "audio": "https:\/\/everyayah.com\/data\/Alafasy_64kbps\/091013.mp3"
  }, {
    "verseId": "14",
    "ayahText": "\u0641\u064e\u0643\u064e\u0630\u0651\u064e\u0628\u064f\u0648\u0652\u0647\u064f \u0641\u064e\u0639\u064e\u0642\u064e\u0631\u064f\u0648\u0652\u0647\u064e\u0627\u06d6 \u0641\u064e\u062f\u064e\u0645\u0652\u062f\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650\u0645\u0652 \u0631\u064e\u0628\u0651\u064f\u0647\u064f\u0645\u0652 \u0628\u0650\u0630\u064e\u0646\u0652\u06e2\u0628\u0650\u0647\u0650\u0645\u0652 \u0641\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0648\u0651\u0670\u0649\u0647\u064e\u0627\u06d6 \ufd3f \u06f1\u06f4 \ufd3e",
    "indoText": "Namun mereka mendustakannya dan menyembelihnya, karena itu Tuhan membinasakan mereka karena dosanya, lalu diratakan-Nya (dengan tanah),",
    "enText": "But they denied him and hamstrung her. So their Lord brought down upon them destruction for their sin and made it equal [upon all of them].",
    "readText": "fa ka\u017c\u017cab\u1ee5hu fa 'aqar\u1ee5h\u0101 fa damdama 'alaihim rabbuhum bi\u017cambihim fa saww\u0101h\u0101",
    "surah_info": "(Qs.Asy-Syams 91:14)",
    "audio": "https:\/\/everyayah.com\/data\/Alafasy_64kbps\/091014.mp3"
  }, {
    "verseId": "15",
    "ayahText": "\u0648\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0627 \u064a\u064e\u062e\u064e\u0627\u0641\u064f \u0639\u064f\u0642\u0652\u0628\u0670\u0647\u064e\u0627 \ufd3f \u06f1\u06f5 \ufd3e",
    "indoText": "dan Dia tidak takut terhadap akibatnya.",
    "enText": "And He does not fear the consequence thereof.",
    "readText": "wa l\u0101 yakh\u0101fu 'uqb\u0101h\u0101",
    "surah_info": "(Qs.Asy-Syams 91:15)",
    "audio": "https:\/\/everyayah.com\/data\/Alafasy_64kbps\/091015.mp3"
  }]
}